into CafÃ© Nervosa.

20:54.860 --> 20:58.057
You were apologising for the way
you've treated me this week.

20:58.366 --> 21:01.438
I'm sorry about that.
Just forget about it, all right?

21:01.747 --> 21:05.535
And something about a raise...

21:07.047 --> 21:09.925
- You're winging it now.
- Am I that transparent?

21:10.219 --> 21:12.574
No, I'm psychic.

21:12.849 --> 21:17.604
The boys are taking us out
to Hoppy's Old Heidelberg for dinner.

21:17.982 --> 21:20.371
Oh, great. German food!

21:20.653 --> 21:25.773
We whip the Jerries twice this century,
and they still have the last laugh.

21:26.162 --> 21:27.914
Dad, sorry, I can't give you a ride.

21:28.875 --> 21:31.309
- I'll give him a lift.
- Ah.

21:32.423 --> 21:35.859
I've enjoyed
getting together with you for coffee.

21:36.179 --> 21:40.377
- What do you talk about all the time?
- Sports, chicks, monster truck rallies.

21:40.728 --> 21:43.083
OK, don't tell me.

21:45.736 --> 21:51.094
Zimbabwe, decaf, non-fat milk,
no cinnamon in sight. Now...

21:51.495 --> 21:53.213
Are you happy?

21:55.794 --> 22:00.584
You know, in the greater
scheme of things, yes, I'd say I am.

